Let’s not forget that the spell that Caleb used to convince Essik was his big floating cat’s paw.

Shadowhand Essik took one look at this ginger skinny thirty-something with new threads and a love of felines and thought: ah, yes. I will teach him the ancient magics.

i forgot,,,, he could fucking do any...
body:
vax is trying to cast locate object and i had some Thoughts, in the following order:

  1. i forgot,,,, he could fucking do any magic,,,,, (outside of his niche paladin shit like bless and smite and lay on hands)
  2. i remembered that time he used dimension door and almost killed the whole party
  3. i concluded he should stop using magic unless the raven queen is there to carefully guide his hand
